OL,6,FHis daughter, Clare Mcallister added:
OL,7,F"You just keep asking yourself
OL,8,Factually, why, why, why do they keep
OL,9,Frejecting us all the time? It's very
OL,10,Fhard to understand."
OL,12,FShe added: "It's just so cruel to be
OL,13,Fhonest. These men - they were just
OL,14,Fdoing what they could to help their
OL,15,Ffellow islanders. It's just so sad
OL,16,Freally."
OL,18,FIn a statement given to the States,
OL,19,Fthe President of Policy and Resources
OL,20,FDeputy Lyndon Trott said the decision
OL,21,Fhad been made following legal advice.
